      <prop type="x-translation-ref">狼跋.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>狼跋其胡，載疐其尾。公孫碩膚，赤舄几几。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The wolf springs forward on his dewlap,
Or trips back on his tail.
The duke was humble, and greatly admirable,
Self-composed in his red slippers.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
